Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready to explain the difference between causality and creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to go back to the beginning of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We have quite a project for this afternoon, don't we? Explain existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and how this all came about. If you go back to the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.79,0:00:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,which anybody here can do through simple meditation, you will see that there are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,various levels. Reality starts out at its highest level as the what Krishna would call the supreme
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,spirit. The Buddha would call the void. Christianity would call Godhead. This is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of the unmanifest. The level of the unmanifest appears as nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,actually. It is allness. It is actually no thingness, however. It has the capacity to become
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. All right, so the unmanifest is the infinite potentiality of divinity beyond form.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Advanced theoretical physics states that in one cubic centimeter of empty space, the potential
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:02:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,centimeter of empty space is equivalent to greater than the total mass of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe, as you're aware, is expanding at the speed of light. As it expands at the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,speed of light, the infinite potential energy within that cubic centimeter of space also
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,expands at an infinite rate. Consequently, the infinite potentiality always balances
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the manifest. Out of that which is unmanifest, and it says in Genesis, in the beginning there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,was the void, no thingness, arises awareness, arises consciousness, and consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of the patterning of form. So the manifest is the outcome from the unmanifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:03:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does reality arise? The unmanifest becomes manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it does so by virtue not of causality, but of creation. So there's a great leap in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness here at this level of consciousness. Nothing within the manifest universe has intrinsic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,power. Nothing in this universe can create its own existence. No rock can will itself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.38,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,into being a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So we would say, the primordial, the unmanifest, is the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So we would say the primordial, the unmanifest, is the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So we would say the primordial, the unmanifest, is the universe. So we would say the primordial,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,intrinsic, basic, initial action, if you will, of the unmanifest, the supreme beingness of the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,universe, was to move from unmanifest to manifest. As it does, if you meditate yourself, let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,back in the other direction. We went from the unmanifest to the manifest domain, down to the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness, going through awareness, consciousness itself, the witness, the observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the experiencer. Let's go back in the other direction, as you would in meditation. In
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,meditation, you notice that thoughts are going through the mind, sensations through the physical
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,body, and with a little bit of observation, you will see that you are not the thoughts. The
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts come and go, but the you remains the same. You'll notice the same thing about the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,body. If the body has sensation, parts of the body may come and go, but the you is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is still the same. If we amputate one leg, the guy still says, I'm me. If we amputate the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,other leg, he's still me. If we take off two arms, he still says, I'm me. So the I-ness, that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I, then, is obviously not the physical body, or it would actually diminish as we chop off arms and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,legs. I lost a thumb one time. I went bye-bye. It's waiting for me in heaven. Bye-bye. And I still
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,felt like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,me. So me minus the thumb, I just felt like me. So me was really unaffected. The sense of I-ness,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then, does not reside within the physical body. When you go to see somebody in there asleep, you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,leave and you say, well, he wasn't there. Did you see Joe? No, he was asleep. So obviously, Joe is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,not his body, because you saw Joe's body lying there. If Joe was his body, you'd say, yeah, I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,saw Joe. You'd say, no, I didn't see Joe. He was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So obviously, you're not your body, that which is you, that which is I, the self, is not the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the mind is also a very transitory thing. So if you just close your eyes and witness what
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:06:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,goes on in meditation, you're aware that these thoughts, like fish, are going through the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You observe now that something is observing the fish. So beyond the content of the ego is the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,observer. How do you know what's going on in your thoughts? How do you know what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only because there's an observer there and there's an experiencer. So there's that which
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the self manifesting as the observer, the witness. And beyond that is the watcher. The
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,watcher watches all this. And the watcher is unaffected by what it watches. So you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness is impersonal. To become enlightened, you have to get rid of the thought that there's a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a separate thing called I that's unique in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just meditate for a short while, you'll see that witnessing is not a personal phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're witnessing whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Try telling yourself, telling your mind, stop witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes right down to witnessing, you don't have any control of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, you will quickly discover that consciousness is impersonal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never even decided that you have consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When you woke up as a small baby, there it was, looking at your little toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity, consciousness then is self-existent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The unmanifest comes to manifest, it first expresses itself as consciousness awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,before it even begins to come into form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we will observe that evolution occurs on the level of consciousness and then manifests
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,within the physical being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we will observe that evolution occurs on the level of consciousness and then manifests within the physical being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we will observe that evolution occurs on the level of consciousness and then manifests within the physical being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Evolution does not occur as a physicality creating a different physicality, creating
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a different physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the level of the invisible domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Within the invisible domain of consciousness, evolution of consciousness evolves and then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it manifests within the physical domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What we see in the physical domain then is the physicality, the externalization, the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of the unmanifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say the divinity within of the self with a capital L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Empire State Building did not arise on 34th Street, it arose within the concept of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,its designer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One day he got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tallest building in the world, or not 34th Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There it was born, in the invisible domain of the consciousness of its creator, who then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,excited people with this concept, excited people with this vision, think what it will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,do for the city of New York, think of the rentals we get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the contractors, the designers, the sculptors, the stonemasons, the steelworkers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all got involved and the banks got excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The lawyers got in there and the real estate appeared and it became manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But as you see, it went from the unmanifest, from the invisible domain, directly into the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,34th Street did not evolve into the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to overcome another delusion of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like us all to be aware that God is at the top of this chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that way to God, and this way to the other place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We laugh at it, but do you realize that a good part of the world, especially throughout
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,history, has had it in the opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It has.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That the force of creation comes from the bottom and goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now when we understand the material world, we realize it has no power of creation within
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical world can create anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a chair in here that can create another chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation comes from power to lesser power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As we see, the bottom is lesser power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The physicality has no power of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical world arises out of the invisible domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That brings us up to sort of defining the nature of God then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's clarify something about God and clarify another great misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,1.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The human ego
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,God has been greatly maligned throughout history, and the human ego is what's from 200 down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:11:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the human ego has to do with revenge, retaliation, jealousy, competitiveness, sensitivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,paranoia, rage, revenge, destructiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the level of demons, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the level of angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Angels are this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They're this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Devils are that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get clear about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout time, because man didn't know much about anything, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Man really didn't know much about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Still doesn't, probably, on the grand time scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, our present life is only written within 100 years, you know, and I've lived
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,through a good part of it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, radios were brand new when I hit this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less TV or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we consider the modern world is really just the way it is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The modern world is really just the last second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout most of mankind, human life throughout history, we said the consciousness level of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,every century was about 190, which is below truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Below truth is easy to sell people that which is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is most prevalent and still exists considerably in large parts of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,including our own country, in certain branches of certain religions, is the confusion of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,God with the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The human ego tends to blame God for its own creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,War is an invention of the human ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not of divine origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the difficulty with a person who is well into the 400s, which is the intellect,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the advanced intellect, is that the negative depictions of God have made atheists of many
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,honest men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They know intuitively that God couldn't be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe in a God who is arbitrary, vengeful, savage, angry, fitful, paranoid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,jealous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens, Freud was correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud and God monotheism.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud said that God was a projection from the human unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he made a mistake and he said, and therefore there isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Freud calibrates at 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The leading scientists in the history, Sir Isaac Newton, Sigmund Freud, Einstein, they
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,all calibrated 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great big block to get from 499, which is the intellect, to 500, which is the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very hard to make that jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In our society, it's very seldom made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,0.4% of the population ever gets from their mind, from their head, into the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So Freud made the mistake in thinking, if there is no false gods, therefore there are
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,no true gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What he should have said was, the negative gods, the gods who kill you and savage you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and throw you into hell forever, are a projection from man's unconsciousness out of his guilt,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,out of his guilt and fear he rejects onto deity, which he really knows nothing about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,unless he's experienced the presence of God, his own imaginations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung went beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung affirmed the spiritual reality of man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,540.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein, Freud is at 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung affirmed the reality of man's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates at 540.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So the correct conclusion is, if the negative gods are really man's imagination, projections
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of his own unconscious guilt and fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,then the real god must be something beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If a false god is all that is negative, then a real god must be something that is rather positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, probably to this audience that seems rather obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you look throughout mankind's history, you'll see that is not obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The negative gods, all kinds of sacrifices made to them, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I had a catatonic patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't spoken in years and he was laying on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was pretty telepathic in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you some of my own experiences later to explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, there was a period of years where I was extremely telepathic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So this catatonic is laying on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't spoken in 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to specialize in schizophrenia and they brought patients from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So this guy got flown in from someplace, Hamburg or Paris or someplace, wrapped up in wet sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And he laid on the floor in this catatonic stupor, mute, wouldn't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, I just sort of looked at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, well, God, what do you want me to do with this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And telepathically, I got what was going on with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And telepathically, I answered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, you're blaming God for the machinations of the ego, productions of your own ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And he jumped off the floor and he started talking and the nurse about fell over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the reason I knew it is because I might as well tell you my own spiritual experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.00,0:16:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sort of comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had been through something of the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So I intuited exactly where he was at.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at a rather young age, I had a lot of unusual spiritual experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And after a number of them, one of them was I was standing out in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly out of nowhere came a vision of the totality of human suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, in its complete entirety and totality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like some infinite part of consciousness to which I was connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Which was capable of comprehending some such a great immensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So this, it was non-intellectual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the sameness of the totality of the suffering of all mankind throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so staggering that I instantly became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, any God that could allow this cannot be a God to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So goodbye, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a rabid atheist, a very devout atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got straight A's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Theology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was always interested in the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this, to attribute a negativity to God is to totally misconceive of the nature of God, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is unmanifest, that which is unmanifest, which radiates forth its infinite potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and calibrates in extreme high numbers, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is the level of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows nothing of human frailty, couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And much less would feel offended and have to, you know, seek revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,To seek revenge, your consciousness would have to be 200 below.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you would first of all have to see yourself as a separate entity who is vulnerable to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would mean you're not divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So anything that seeks revenge cannot be divinity by definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth of that which you are is absolutely invulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Unassailable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, we did mention a few things that made these kind of subjects perhaps interesting to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the radio today for a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a good thing to do before you're going to give up all of your drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it came out that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So from 9 to 11, I had a two-hour program.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And they asked me about some of these things and so I know what they were interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll just say them to you because you're not asking questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I could just hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But the interesting thing about this particular lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, everybody in the audience presumes there's a Dr. Hawkins here speaking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When you stop identifying yourself as a physicality or a specific ego or locality,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,then what you realize, what exists is consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way it came about in my own experience was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was about three, when I was about three years old, there was no awareness of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly at age three, there was a profound confrontation with existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no words for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not a verbal experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a stunning awareness of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And instantly came its dualistic opposite, nonexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, I saw the dilemma of existence versus nonexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it became obvious that if I exist, the potentiality had been there for me not to have existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And so out of assuming I existed, because that seemed to be what was going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there came the possibility of nonexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was the conflict that so-called duality of existence versus nonexistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To solve that duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness has to be around 850 or 900 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The duality of existence versus nonexistence doesn't even come up to about 850 or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, this was a profound confrontation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and it really was the setting of the spiritual lesson project,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual project of this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in teenage years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the personal individual self,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if I thought, who am I,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,would begin to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was just an infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And that would sort of scare me that my self is disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I would cling to my personal self and give it lots of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and think the word David sitting in his seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was pretty bright also at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I graduated at the end of my class in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a straight A in crayons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, so I had these peculiar phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which I never talked to anybody about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was around 12 or 13,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a huge paper route in Wisconsin,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,18 miles, the biggest in the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was out in the sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And one time it was like 20 below zero on a blizzard,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got caught in this blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was many miles from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I dug into a snow bank to stay out of the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 20 below.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was ferocious out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I snuck into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In Wisconsin, the snow bank's by the side of the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, about 15, 20 feet high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.20,0:22:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I dug a hole into this snow bank
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to get in out of this fierce wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my knees were frozen stiff,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and my pants were stiff,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and they even cracked instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I climbed into this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And before long,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the most exquisite experience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,came upon, came about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Any personal self disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,only an infinite, growing presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all time and all space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the knowingness that that which I was experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.10,0:22:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which I am are one and the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all time before all universes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,before all thoughts and worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Long after all universes come and go,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which I am exists beyond all time and space.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is all wordless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind was silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And the exquisiteness of it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.28,0:23:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And every time it recurred,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the same exquisite disinclination
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to reactivate the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,re-identify with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd have no idea how much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all out of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and timeless experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The next thing was my father shaking my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd finally come out in our 29 model 8 Ford
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to find him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.92,0:23:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to find his son who was lost in the blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I looked at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw that if I did not come in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,in the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.37,0:23:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,he would presume I'd died,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that the body would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And he would be very upset by this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because he believed that I am my body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and he believes he's his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so he believed I'm my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I didn't resume it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he would go into enormous grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:23:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I love my father a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.44,0:24:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So for his sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.85,0:24:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which I've sort of since regretted,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.36,0:24:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.36,0:24:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back in the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I tried to acclimatize myself
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to how the world sees reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.36,0:24:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never spoke of this to anybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next time it happened again,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,one time it happened with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.52,0:24:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing a technique called rebirthing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.52,0:24:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I went out of body
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.52,0:24:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with the same infinite glowing infinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.52,0:24:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had no decision to breathe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.81,0:24:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.81,0:24:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that this was going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.81,0:24:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,very upsetting to my rebirther,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.81,0:24:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,who was going to lose his first subject in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.81,0:24:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I could see the headlines,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.81,0:24:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.81,0:24:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,telepathically, he's saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.81,0:24:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,breathe, hey, breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You should love me, breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.81,0:24:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.81,0:24:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just really loved him intensely,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.81,0:24:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and frankly, I did breathe for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:24:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.81,0:24:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hang him up with a dead body here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And see, because the world consumes that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.81,0:25:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when this stops breathing in and out and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.81,0:25:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.81,0:25:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this is very naive,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.81,0:25:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's the way the world sees things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.81,0:25:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have to go along with the world
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.81,0:25:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of humor it in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.97,0:25:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And in 1965,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.97,0:25:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a state of incredible despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.97,0:25:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget I was an atheist at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.97,0:25:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and a very devout one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.97,0:25:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a devout atheist, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.16,0:25:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was against these negative gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.16,0:25:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and wasn't really an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.38,0:25:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just against all these concepts of God
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.38,0:25:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.51,0:25:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any positive concept of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.51,0:25:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but I knew that whatever people believed in
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.51,0:25:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't hang in with my experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.51,0:25:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.51,0:25:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was at the depths of spiritual despair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.51,0:25:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and physically ill
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.51,0:25:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and in a catastrophic state.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.51,0:25:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went into a state of black despair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:26:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.18,0:26:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's really levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.18,0:26:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.18,0:26:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of levels of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.50,0:26:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the higher levels
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.50,0:26:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,where you're being tortured and fried and all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.50,0:26:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that's just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.50,0:26:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.50,0:26:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you go to an existential despair
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.50,0:26:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the blackness is beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.50,0:26:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.50,0:26:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.50,0:26:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hold my breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.50,0:26:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all right, I'd ask his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.50,0:26:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.50,0:26:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, before you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.50,0:26:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you go on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.50,0:26:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably best to play it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.50,0:26:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the other side,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.50,0:26:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.50,0:26:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.50,0:26:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.50,0:26:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.20,0:26:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.43,0:26:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As a profound atheist,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.43,0:26:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I really did not hold my breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.43,0:26:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I was going to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.43,0:26:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.43,0:26:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,hollering down an empty alleyway there,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.43,0:26:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's nobody there to hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.43,0:26:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.43,0:26:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's on the record that you did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.43,0:27:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hollered down the empty alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.43,0:27:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then everything disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.00,0:27:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.00,0:27:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have no idea how much time went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.04,0:27:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But on January 10, 1965 then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.04,0:27:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly that which had been David,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.04,0:27:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that which the world calls David,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.04,0:27:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,disappeared completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.04,0:27:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no individual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.04,0:27:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.04,0:27:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.04,0:27:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an infinite presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.51,0:27:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,which is and still is all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.51,0:27:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It expresses itself
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.51,0:27:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,as the creation observed and witnessed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.51,0:27:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,by the senses,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.51,0:27:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but the divinity of its nature
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.51,0:27:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is shown forth with a radiance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.51,0:27:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that is so stunning as to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.51,0:27:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,leave no question.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.99,0:27:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the body went about its own business,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.99,0:27:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,which it still does.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.99,0:27:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.99,0:27:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it moves and it's like a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.99,0:27:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.99,0:27:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it runs itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.99,0:27:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with the person itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.99,0:27:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,People think,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.12,0:28:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I decided to move my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.12,0:28:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.12,0:28:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the arm moved itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.12,0:28:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and then instantly the ego jumps in
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.12,0:28:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and says,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.12,0:28:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.12,0:28:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.12,0:28:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It moved itself before the eye says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.12,0:28:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In meditation you can discover that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So this body was there
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.18,0:28:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,like another piece of furniture in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.18,0:28:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I really had no interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.18,0:28:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mind had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.18,0:28:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no thinkingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.18,0:28:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything happened of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in this infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.88,0:28:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that condition lasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.88,0:28:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't possible to think in words.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.88,0:28:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No words came forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.88,0:28:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All that is is known forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.95,0:28:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and to understand one grain of sand
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.95,0:28:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is to understand the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.95,0:28:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's nothing you need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.95,0:28:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,because once you are all that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.95,0:28:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.95,0:28:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sense of completeness was present.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.33,0:28:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To this day there's nothing I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.16,0:29:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People say,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.16,0:29:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you want for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.16,0:29:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.16,0:29:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to win the lottery?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.20,0:29:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to win the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.20,0:29:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's absolutely nothing I need or want.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.20,0:29:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because once you are all that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.20,0:29:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.20,0:29:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And if there's nothing lacking,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.20,0:29:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there's obviously nothing you would gain
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.20,0:29:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,by getting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.20,0:29:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So there was the loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.29,0:29:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing that happened
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.29,0:29:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,was the loss of all the drives
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.29,0:29:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that are considered human.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.29,0:29:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The desire for success,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.29,0:29:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for money,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.29,0:29:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,for security.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.39,0:29:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All the things that people consider
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.39,0:29:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,important in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.39,0:29:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly became meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.39,0:29:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And so by ordinary human standards
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.39,0:29:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was motivationless.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.39,0:29:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No motivation for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.06,0:29:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the body went about its way,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.06,0:29:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,which it still does.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.06,0:29:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a karmic wind-up toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.06,0:29:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.06,0:29:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my little friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.06,0:29:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of times I wish it had fur.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.06,0:29:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.06,0:29:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you know if this thing had fur
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.06,0:29:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like it a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.06,0:29:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be more fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.06,0:29:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,like a kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.06,0:29:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.06,0:29:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So this thing is my happy puppet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.06,0:29:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it goes about its business.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.06,0:30:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been doing that since 1965 by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.06,0:30:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.25,0:30:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It just does whatever it's going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.25,0:30:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So that condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.05,0:30:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that condition then was difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.05,0:30:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to function in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.05,0:30:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And actually I did leave the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.05,0:30:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a huge practice in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.05,0:30:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I moved to a small town
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.05,0:30:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,where I lived by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.05,0:30:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a monastery for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.05,0:30:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a monastery for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.21,0:30:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I lost identification
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.21,0:30:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.21,0:30:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can remember one time
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.21,0:30:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't eaten for some days either.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.21,0:30:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a hard thing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.21,0:30:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,for me to do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.21,0:30:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I walked past the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.21,0:30:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was somebody in the house with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.21,0:30:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave me a mental shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.21,0:30:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this person walking through the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.37,0:30:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and realized it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.37,0:30:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.37,0:30:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was shocking for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.37,0:30:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.37,0:30:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so the loss of identification with physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.37,0:30:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're saying is that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.50,0:31:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in certain peculiar persons then
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.53,0:31:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this spontaneous occurrence
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.53,0:31:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that also occurs as a result of meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.53,0:31:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had done Zen meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.53,0:31:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and some things before that experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.53,0:31:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.98,0:31:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,one can transcend the identification
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.98,0:31:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,with the linear world,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.98,0:31:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the Newtonian paradigm of reality
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.98,0:31:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and shift to the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.98,0:31:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.98,0:31:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what the world considers spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.98,0:31:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is really just the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.98,0:31:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And what it considers material
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.98,0:31:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.98,0:31:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the two coincide.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.40,0:31:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.40,0:31:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a linear reality here,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.40,0:31:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the chairs and the desks and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.40,0:31:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this is all here within space.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.40,0:31:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can identify either with the chairs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.40,0:31:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the physicality
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.40,0:31:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or as what happened to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.46,0:31:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the space
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.46,0:31:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in which all of this occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.46,0:31:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.46,0:31:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the panorama,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.46,0:31:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.46,0:31:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the movie of what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.46,0:32:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,comes and goes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.46,0:32:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and it actually has no effect on me whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.46,0:32:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually it's amusing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.46,0:32:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,if anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.46,0:32:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So for some years
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.46,0:32:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I had trouble communicating with the world
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.46,0:32:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because the mind is silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.46,0:32:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,which it is to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.46,0:32:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am is silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.46,0:32:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It says nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.46,0:32:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was having to learn how to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.32,0:32:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which people would say things
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.32,0:32:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and it didn't make any...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.32,0:32:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean they would talk
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.32,0:32:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and it made no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.32,0:32:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was totally irrelevant
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.32,0:32:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and not even believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.32,0:32:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I found that within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.32,0:32:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I would ask the spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.32,0:32:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.32,0:32:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I would get what that meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.32,0:32:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was like a translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.32,0:32:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A translator within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.32,0:32:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that would transform
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.32,0:32:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what is being said
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.32,0:32:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world of form
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.32,0:32:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so it was comprehensible
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.32,0:32:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world of non-form.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.32,0:32:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way I can explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.32,0:32:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.12,0:32:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So this then has to do
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.12,0:32:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with the two different dimensions
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.12,0:32:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in which life can be experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.12,0:32:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,from the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.12,0:32:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and from the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.12,0:33:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How to move from the linear domain
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.12,0:33:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,into the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We talk about that as spiritual work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.12,0:33:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual work, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.12,0:33:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual work is merely a willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.12,0:33:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,People say,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.12,0:33:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I evolve
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.12,0:33:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in my level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.12,0:33:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very simple, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.12,0:33:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Choice is here at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.12,0:33:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And what we do is
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.12,0:33:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we choose to be forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.12,0:33:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We choose to be helpful to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.16,0:33:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all options
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.16,0:33:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that are available to us at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.16,0:33:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to be kind and considerate
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.89,0:33:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.89,0:33:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,from moment to moment
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.89,0:33:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,within and without.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.89,0:33:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be kind and forgiving
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.89,0:33:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,means towards yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.89,0:33:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as to everything that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.89,0:33:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.89,0:33:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody asked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.42,0:33:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you define God?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.42,0:33:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, well, in my experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.42,0:34:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.70,0:34:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to manifest existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.70,0:34:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.28,0:34:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,within itself to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.28,0:34:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have enough power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.60,0:34:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have within itself
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.92,0:34:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.92,0:34:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is unmanifest then,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.92,0:34:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is the source of existence itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.98,0:34:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask, where is God?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.04,0:34:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the capacity to exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.94,0:34:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.94,0:34:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most direct manifestation
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.94,0:34:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.94,0:34:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.94,0:34:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So the current book I'm writing on
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.22,0:34:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is called
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.22,0:34:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eye of the Eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.22,0:34:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,spelled E-Y-E of the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.22,0:34:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eye of the Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.22,0:34:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.41,0:34:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.41,0:34:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,when you say eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.41,0:34:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you mean by eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.41,0:34:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean your physical body?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.41,0:34:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.41,0:34:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the eye owns your physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.41,0:34:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.41,0:35:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that allows us to say eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.79,0:35:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The person assumes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.79,0:35:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is an individual,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.79,0:35:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,specific thing called eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.04,0:35:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a me, me, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This eye, this self,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.36,0:35:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and that it's temporal,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.36,0:35:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's temporary,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.36,0:35:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody therefore fears death
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.36,0:35:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.36,0:35:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,well, when you croak,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.46,0:35:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,say goodbye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.62,0:35:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.84,0:35:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, there is an infinite eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.90,0:35:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When we say consciousness itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.09,0:35:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness itself is a quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.09,0:35:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,impersonal quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.09,0:35:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,within your own consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.09,0:35:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,which accounts for your awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.09,0:35:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,your capacity to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.35,0:35:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to know that you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.35,0:35:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming out of an impersonal quality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.35,0:35:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,called consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.35,0:35:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This consciousness manifests itself
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.35,0:35:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in the belief, mistakenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.35,0:36:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are a very limited thing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.35,0:36:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that just got here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.35,0:36:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and is going to be leaving
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.35,0:36:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,before a few years,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.35,0:36:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and you had a beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.35,0:36:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you will end
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.35,0:36:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in this physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.66,0:36:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That which really says eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.66,0:36:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,if you do it just,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.66,0:36:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't take very long in meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.66,0:36:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,to go to the source
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.66,0:36:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of what is it that is saying eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.66,0:36:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What enables you to even say
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.66,0:36:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that you exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.66,0:36:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That the capacity to say personal eye
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.12,0:36:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is coming from the endowment
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.12,0:36:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of an impersonal eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.12,0:36:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The impersonal eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.12,0:36:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the same in all of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the self and me with a capital S,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.12,0:36:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same as the self
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.12,0:36:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.12,0:36:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.12,0:36:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have agreement on that, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.86,0:36:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We do agree we all exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.86,0:36:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We do agree that there is a capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.40,0:36:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to know that one exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.40,0:37:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.44,0:37:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot really prove that you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.44,0:37:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put forth all kinds of data
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.44,0:37:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and that will impress people
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.44,0:37:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in the low of the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.44,0:37:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as convincing logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.44,0:37:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.44,0:37:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to exist is a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.44,0:37:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.56,0:37:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so science will take us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.30,0:37:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But we notice that the level of the intellect
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.30,0:37:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.30,0:37:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The 400s, things always act mysteriously too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.55,0:37:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they are wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.48,0:37:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you see here the,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.48,0:37:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a little thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.48,0:37:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,a little light thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.48,0:37:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably doesn't work either.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.48,0:37:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it does work.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.40,0:37:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how it works,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.40,0:37:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but you push a button and it lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.72,0:37:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.17,0:37:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, the world of thingness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.17,0:37:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,has not been my,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.26,0:37:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.26,0:37:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as lazy as I think
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.26,0:37:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,how it operates or what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.26,0:38:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you see that the level of science
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.68,0:38:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.41,0:38:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, science then is capable
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.41,0:38:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,of understanding logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.41,0:38:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only thing with man's knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.41,0:38:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,is people don't put the limits on,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.41,0:38:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the limits on their knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.41,0:38:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Science cannot say anything about
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.41,0:38:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the nonlinear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.41,0:38:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no validity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.05,0:38:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what science says
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.05,0:38:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,about spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has no capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.05,0:38:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to comprehend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.05,0:38:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't have the slightest idea
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.05,0:38:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,where to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.05,0:38:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise, it's best
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.79,0:38:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that spirituality stays out of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.79,0:38:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When the church makes pronouncements
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.98,0:38:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,about Galileo and the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.46,0:38:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,going around the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.46,0:38:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the earth going around the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.46,0:38:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's out of its bailiwick.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.46,0:38:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And you like having an opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.46,0:38:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on outside matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.46,0:38:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing that's beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.52,0:38:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,about the 12-step programs
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.52,0:38:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is the purity of the spiritual essence of it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.52,0:38:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is that they have no opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.52,0:38:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on outside matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.52,0:38:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.52,0:39:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you're driving along,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.72,0:39:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,just think how relieving it is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.72,0:39:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,not to have any opinion about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.72,0:39:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I don't have to have an opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.72,0:39:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.72,0:39:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a relief, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.72,0:39:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really need an opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.72,0:39:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,about anything, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.72,0:39:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's great not to have
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.72,0:39:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,any opinions about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.72,0:39:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One way to tell whether you're making
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.58,0:39:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,good spiritual progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.58,0:39:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and here's a very good test,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.58,0:39:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is if you enjoy letting somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.58,0:39:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,get ahead of you in traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.58,0:39:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get like a feel-good glow,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.84,0:39:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,come on in, fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.84,0:39:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.87,0:39:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, the person goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.87,0:39:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.87,0:39:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see them fall over, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.87,0:39:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little bit of love
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.87,0:39:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,knocks people out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.87,0:39:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You come up to the stoplight,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.03,0:39:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,look at the person in the next car
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.03,0:39:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and smile at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.03,0:39:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, it causes terror and panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.03,0:39:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Call 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.92,0:39:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a man smiling here in the next car.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.92,0:39:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure they're not the opposite sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.92,0:40:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.92,0:40:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.92,0:40:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe even the same sex nowadays,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.92,0:40:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.92,0:40:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best not to smile at strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.92,0:40:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you see
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.05,0:40:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.05,0:40:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,become sort of automatic
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.05,0:40:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,once you're familiar with certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.05,0:40:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the things we've talked about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.05,0:40:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your consciousness is not the same as it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.05,0:40:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that it's on a trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.05,0:40:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how this consciousness works.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.05,0:40:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,These energy fields in chaos theory
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.05,0:40:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and chaos theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.05,0:40:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,nonlinear dynamics theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.05,0:40:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,are organized around an attractor field.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.21,0:40:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,These levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.21,0:40:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,dominate the human mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.21,0:40:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind, like, picks up
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.21,0:40:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and is entrained
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.21,0:40:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,by these powerful energy fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.47,0:40:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The field holds dominion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.47,0:40:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,over man's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.63,0:40:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you ascribe to a certain attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.63,0:41:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you now become subject to being dominated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.63,0:41:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,by the entire set of attitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.63,0:41:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that go with that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.65,0:41:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you give a lot of energy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.97,0:41:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to right and wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.97,0:41:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you are now stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.97,0:41:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right and wrong is one of the great dualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.97,0:41:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But to become involved spiritually,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.97,0:41:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.97,0:41:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and see right and wrong are very irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.97,0:41:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It really makes no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.97,0:41:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,whether the thing is right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.97,0:41:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you jump that duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.97,0:41:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not stuck there,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.97,0:41:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and instantly your consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.97,0:41:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,will rise up into the high five hundreds.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.97,0:41:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The high five hundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.97,0:41:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is not interested in right and wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.97,0:41:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who hand out turkeys at the mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.97,0:41:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't try to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.97,0:41:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,who's justified in having a turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.97,0:41:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not having a turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.97,0:41:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the divinity of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.13,0:41:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the love of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.13,0:41:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,radiates equally on all.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.13,0:41:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't get involved in judgmentalism.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.13,0:41:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.89,0:41:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll just sort of go over them
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.89,0:41:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you get what they're about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.08,0:41:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Very at the lowest we have
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.08,0:41:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.08,0:41:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is a miserable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.08,0:42:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is our view of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.08,0:42:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If your consciousness is down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.08,0:42:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this is how you experience life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.08,0:42:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what life looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.08,0:42:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.08,0:42:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame is the predominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.08,0:42:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And its energy is 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.49,0:42:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you the pictures you see
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.49,0:42:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,on the front of Time magazine
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.49,0:42:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of starving Ethiopian infants
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.52,0:42:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,who are born with AIDS
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.52,0:42:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and have starved to death
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.52,0:42:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,probably by the age of six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.52,0:42:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The mother doesn't even know
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.52,0:42:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what to do with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.52,0:42:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She just leaves it by the side of the road
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.52,0:42:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,where the flies gather on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.52,0:42:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all these people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.42,0:42:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole subcontinents come in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.42,0:42:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at these levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.42,0:42:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough energy to pull
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.42,0:42:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,enough energy from life to even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.42,0:42:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Interestingly enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.83,0:42:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,we can calibrate the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.69,0:42:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of an infant the minute it's born.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.69,0:42:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.36,0:42:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,at a certain level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.36,0:43:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that arise from?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.40,0:43:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness, then, is an ongoing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.44,0:43:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In my own observation,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.44,0:43:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,this is my own observation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.44,0:43:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and my own conclusions
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.44,0:43:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and my own research,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.44,0:43:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that consciousness evolves
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.05,0:43:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,from down here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.05,0:43:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,on up to divinity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.05,0:43:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And it may take many physicalities
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.12,0:43:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.12,0:43:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I view consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.12,0:43:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,as a continuum
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.12,0:43:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that seeks periodically
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.12,0:43:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to physicalize.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.69,0:43:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When we talk about karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.54,0:43:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what we're saying is that
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.54,0:43:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,every action manifests
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.24,0:43:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a vibration or a frequency
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.24,0:43:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,which registers somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.24,0:43:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And this somewhere carries on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.24,0:43:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it has consequences eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.24,0:43:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Every religion says,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.28,0:43:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as you sow, you shall reap.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.28,0:43:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.28,0:43:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'll necessarily physically manifest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.28,0:43:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it does say
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.28,0:43:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're going to go
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.28,0:44:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,from one level to another
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.28,0:44:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and where you go to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.28,0:44:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.28,0:44:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of vibrations you've set up
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.72,0:44:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in your spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.72,0:44:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,your soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.72,0:44:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.33,0:44:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My own view of it is that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.91,0:44:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,these levels here
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.91,0:44:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,really are of the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.04,0:44:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And these,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.68,0:44:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're like a cork.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.68,0:44:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a cork in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.68,0:44:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the sea of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.68,0:44:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your calibrated level determines
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.68,0:44:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,where you rise or fall as a cork.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.68,0:44:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you leave the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.12,0:44:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,this is just,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.12,0:44:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to buy anything I'm saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.12,0:44:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,when you leave the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.12,0:44:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the spirit leaves the body
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.12,0:44:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been out of body
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.12,0:44:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know the spirit does leave the body
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.12,0:44:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've been down there and up there
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.12,0:44:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll look after the body down in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.12,0:44:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And where the spirit goes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.12,0:44:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,would then depend on its vibration,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.12,0:44:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,its buoyancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.12,0:44:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So these frequencies then would determine
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.25,0:44:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is such a thing as a spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.25,0:44:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that supersedes the physicality,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.25,0:44:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,where it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.25,0:45:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where it goes is it would just float
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.25,0:45:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to its own level.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.25,0:45:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This to me is the absolute justice of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.25,0:45:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,God is incapable of injustice
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.25,0:45:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because each one of us by our own actions
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.25,0:45:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,sets our own karmic vibrational pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.25,0:45:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby determines our destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.44,0:45:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in the great beyond,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.44,0:45:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which is actually here,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.44,0:45:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but it sounds like the great beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.44,0:45:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So these people came in here
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.05,0:45:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,at a pretty low level.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.72,0:45:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we see people who see God as condemning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.72,0:45:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here God despises us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.72,0:45:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here God is vindictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.72,0:45:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always getting even with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.72,0:45:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here God is that which condemns you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.76,0:45:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and disdains you and is punitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.76,0:45:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,denies what you need to survive life,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.76,0:45:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is vengeful.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.76,0:45:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see the view of God
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.32,0:45:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.32,0:45:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on your level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.32,0:45:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The life view is life is miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.32,0:45:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an evil world,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.32,0:45:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a hopeless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.32,0:45:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a tragic world,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.32,0:45:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a frightening world,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.32,0:46:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a disappointing world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.32,0:46:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a world of anger,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.32,0:46:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a demanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.36,0:46:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or is it a feasible,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.36,0:46:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,satisfactory,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.36,0:46:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeful world of opportunity?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.36,0:46:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.36,0:46:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,God is either a punitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.36,0:46:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,horrible thing that you live in dread of,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.36,0:46:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or he's the source of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.36,0:46:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,inspiration,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.36,0:46:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,mercy,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.36,0:46:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.36,0:46:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,love,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.36,0:46:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's actually your own self with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.36,0:46:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go through these emotional levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.54,0:46:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We go through these calibrated energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.54,0:46:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and we see the emotion that is associated with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.54,0:46:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Down here we have blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.54,0:46:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,People spend their whole lifetimes blaming everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.54,0:46:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have whole continents.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.60,0:46:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Middle East spent the last couple thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.60,0:46:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,First they blame one,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.60,0:46:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then they blame the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.60,0:46:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They shoot over a bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.60,0:46:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then they retaliate with another bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.60,0:46:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This amuses them by the millennium.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.60,0:46:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They go on for thousands of years doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.76,0:46:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They live off the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.76,0:46:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They live off the energy of hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.76,0:46:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate and blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.76,0:46:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get a little bit better,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.76,0:46:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you go into depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.76,0:47:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out of hate and vindictive killingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.76,0:47:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you lay on the floor and sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.76,0:47:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You at least come up to regret,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.02,0:47:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which is,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.02,0:47:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the beginning of decency,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.02,0:47:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.02,0:47:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,at least you regret that you bombed all those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.02,0:47:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you get a little bit anxious about,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.02,0:47:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,am I doing the right thing or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.02,0:47:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you can get your energy up to cravingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.02,0:47:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the level of the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.02,0:47:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the addictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.02,0:47:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're stuck in the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.02,0:47:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in this wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.02,0:47:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It cannot be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.02,0:47:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cravingness is an energy fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.02,0:47:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you cannot satisfy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.44,0:47:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you get through this,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.44,0:47:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you're planning on the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.11,0:47:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.11,0:47:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get up to the levels of hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.11,0:47:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of pride and scorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.11,0:47:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are what's happening in the process in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.11,0:47:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, what happens is you eliminate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.11,0:47:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Elimination is what happens here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.11,0:47:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.11,0:47:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you get eliminated,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.11,0:47:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you get destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.11,0:48:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,pounded into powder
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.11,0:48:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,before they dump you in the dumpster.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.11,0:48:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have despondency,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.11,0:48:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,withdrawal,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.11,0:48:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,enslavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.11,0:48:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the level of addictions,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.11,0:48:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which many of us work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.11,0:48:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of enslavement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.11,0:48:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hooked in the solar plexus of wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.11,0:48:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no satisfaction for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.11,0:48:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So it goes on and on continually running you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.11,0:48:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're enslaved by cravingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.75,0:48:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred leads to aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.75,0:48:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got Adolf Hitler
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.75,0:48:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and militaristic hateful people
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.75,0:48:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with inflated egos
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.75,0:48:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,who are scornful of others
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.78,0:48:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and live out of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.94,0:48:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Deutschland über alles.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.94,0:48:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Any sane person, when you think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.58,0:48:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you mean, Deutschland über alles?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.58,0:48:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,70 million people bought it
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.58,0:48:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and so they all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.58,0:48:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, so here you have this inflated ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.68,0:48:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, once you get above it,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.84,0:48:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the level of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.84,0:48:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the emotion here is one of affirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.84,0:48:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You take the first step in the 12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.84,0:49:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit the truth about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.84,0:49:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, the minute you admit truth about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.84,0:49:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.48,0:49:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gee, that's a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.67,0:49:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was at the head of my class in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.67,0:49:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.67,0:49:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so affirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.67,0:49:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This leads to trust, optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.67,0:49:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is a very important level for all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.67,0:49:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because many of us work in the health field.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.67,0:49:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.67,0:49:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you see a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.67,0:49:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In comes the kid to your institution
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.67,0:49:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,who's done really awful things
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.67,0:49:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and is awesomely negative,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.67,0:49:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,telling you where to go with their finger
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.67,0:49:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute they say hello to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.37,0:49:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.37,0:49:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to be compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.37,0:49:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the levels of transcendence
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.37,0:49:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.37,0:49:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And we move on up through reverence.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.37,0:49:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The reverence for all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.37,0:49:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The reverence for all that lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.37,0:49:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.37,0:49:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The reverence that the source of existence
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.37,0:49:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.37,0:49:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is divinity itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.14,0:50:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment of revelation was so stunning
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.14,0:50:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just profound.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.14,0:50:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like you walked out of a dark cave
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.68,0:50:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that you lived into all your life
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.68,0:50:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,into a field of snow
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.68,0:50:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in midday.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.68,0:50:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just beyond all comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.45,0:50:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.71,0:50:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All these belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.71,0:50:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,thinking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.74,0:50:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You come into what's called
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.74,0:50:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the ineffable.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.74,0:50:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's called enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.74,0:50:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.74,0:50:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is divine
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.74,0:50:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is the source and the essence
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.74,0:50:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own self
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.74,0:50:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.45,0:50:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The various religions may have confused it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.45,0:50:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,by using different terminology.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.64,0:50:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But in essence all of them say
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.64,0:50:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that the ultimate reality
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.64,0:50:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.64,0:50:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus said where he said it was
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.64,0:50:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,heaven is within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.64,0:50:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.64,0:50:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.64,0:51:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are spiritually committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.22,0:51:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the most intense way
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.22,0:51:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach a state of enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.22,0:51:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or greater awareness?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.64,0:51:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.64,0:51:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,reality can be only discovered
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.64,0:51:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the absolute instant of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.64,0:51:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is in this absolute
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.64,0:51:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,split nanomicrosecond
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.31,0:51:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of now
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.31,0:51:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that the reality shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.31,0:51:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.31,0:51:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is so
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.60,0:51:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,beclouded with clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.60,0:51:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't see
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.60,0:51:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the sun in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.60,0:51:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,except for a split second
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.60,0:51:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,between two clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.66,0:51:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the Buddha said
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.66,0:51:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I discovered that what he said was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.66,0:51:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that the great infinite void
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.66,0:51:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite beingness of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.66,0:51:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the godness, the godhead
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.66,0:51:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the transcendent divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.66,0:51:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of the supreme of all
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.69,0:51:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is found between two thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.17,0:51:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore there are many
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.17,0:51:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,meditative techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.17,0:51:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in which one witnesses the thoughts going by
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.17,0:52:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,stops identifying with them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.30,0:52:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.30,0:52:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,some very exquisite techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.30,0:52:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to do this very thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.30,0:52:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is true, it is within
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.30,0:52:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite presence of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.30,0:52:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does one transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.75,0:52:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite now?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.75,0:52:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You witness out of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.94,0:52:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,how everything is arising
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.94,0:52:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and falling within mind
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.32,0:52:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,like a musical note.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.32,0:52:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When you listen to a note of music
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.39,0:52:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it arises and
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.39,0:52:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,within the creation and experience
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.39,0:52:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of that note is already
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.42,0:52:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it is already disappearing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.42,0:52:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and a new note is already
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.84,0:52:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't get caught in the melody
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.84,0:52:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you stay on the moment of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.84,0:52:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the sound that is arising now
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.84,0:52:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't try to cling to it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.84,0:52:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't try to anticipate the next moment of now
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.84,0:52:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and you discover that what the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.84,0:52:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is trying to do all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.84,0:52:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is anticipate the next split second of now
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.84,0:52:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and control it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.06,0:52:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you watch in meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.06,0:52:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,what your mind is doing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.06,0:53:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is trying to grab the next moment of now
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.06,0:53:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,verbalize it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.98,0:53:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,give it a name, give it an image, give it a form
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.98,0:53:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it is like there is an energy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.11,0:53:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.11,0:53:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,which comes out of a primordial matrix
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.11,0:53:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond form
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.65,0:53:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it is formless
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.65,0:53:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is out of this powerful goo
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.65,0:53:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that wants to constantly come into
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.65,0:53:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,being as a thought
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.65,0:53:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to catch it, the willingness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.65,0:53:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to let go of thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.65,0:53:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you will see that thinkingness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.65,0:53:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is an independent function all its own
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.65,0:53:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no I thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.65,0:53:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as you become enlightened you see there is no individual I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.65,0:53:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no doer behind the doings
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.65,0:53:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no doer doing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.26,0:53:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what is being done now
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.26,0:53:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it is happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.26,0:53:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is the expression
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.26,0:53:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,everything comes into being
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.26,0:53:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as the perfect expression
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.26,0:53:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own essence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.26,0:53:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and it does so in this instant
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.26,0:53:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,each instant it is
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.48,0:53:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it expresses the essence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.48,0:53:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own beingness
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.48,0:54:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,its own reality
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.48,0:54:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is its divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.48,0:54:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so divinity expresses itself
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.48,0:54:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as existence
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.87,0:54:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as beingness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.87,0:54:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is that what you are at this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.87,0:54:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way to catch it at that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.87,0:54:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is to ride the crest
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.09,0:54:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of this exact instant
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.92,0:54:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be a nano instant
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.92,0:54:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I like nano, that is a new one
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.92,0:54:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I always liked micro
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.63,0:54:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is another one used in astronomy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.63,0:54:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning even lower than micro
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.63,0:54:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget what it is now
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.98,0:54:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but nano seems like the greatest
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.98,0:54:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the littlest of the littlest
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.98,0:54:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just love the thought
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.98,0:54:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is nano manufacturing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.98,0:54:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,going on
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.98,0:54:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,little molecules can be taught
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.98,0:54:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,how to make themselves into a little factory
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.98,0:54:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and create I guess a whole Ford automobile
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.98,0:54:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.98,0:54:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.08,0:54:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there is a meditative technique
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.08,0:54:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which you can do throughout the day
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.56,0:54:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what you are doing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.56,0:55:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,one is always
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.62,0:55:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,as you look about you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.62,0:55:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there is your macular vision
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.62,0:55:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and your peripheral vision
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.62,0:55:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,macular vision is the center
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.00,0:55:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when you have intention about something
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.00,0:55:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the macula of the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.10,0:55:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is focusing on a specific point
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.10,0:55:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because you are going to do something with it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.10,0:55:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you are going to eat it, kill it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.10,0:55:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,mate with it, buy it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.64,0:55:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,store it, paint it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.95,0:55:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the peripheral vision is only aware
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.95,0:55:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of your general positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.95,0:55:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in life
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.95,0:55:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the more spiritually evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.27,0:55:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you get, the more you tend to live
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.27,0:55:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in peripheral vision
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.27,0:55:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,what is going on in macular vision
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.27,0:55:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes less and less important
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.27,0:55:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it is just the work of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.27,0:55:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the more detached you become
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.46,0:55:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the details of what is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.46,0:55:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes less and less important
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.46,0:55:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what is important is the essence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.46,0:55:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you do that yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.49,0:55:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when you walk into a room
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.49,0:55:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you are aware of two things
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.49,0:56:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you are aware of what you are looking at
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.49,0:56:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are also quickly getting the whole deal
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.49,0:56:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.49,0:56:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the size of the amphitheater
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.49,0:56:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood of finding a seat
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.49,0:56:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the type of a crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.49,0:56:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.49,0:56:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,all the boards go by
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.49,0:56:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and bushes go by
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.49,0:56:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and you don't get caught in any of them
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.49,0:56:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are aware that something
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.49,0:56:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that is not any of that out there
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.49,0:56:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is witnessing all that out there
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.49,0:56:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and that type of meditation brings you to
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.49,0:56:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness that there is something witnessing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.49,0:56:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that witnessing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.49,0:56:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,is happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.49,0:56:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it is totally impersonal
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.49,0:56:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no personal eye that is witnessing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.49,0:56:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,any more than there is a personal eye
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.49,0:56:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,making your body do what it is doing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.49,0:56:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I caught the body
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.49,0:56:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in a trick
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.49,0:56:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I caught the ego one time
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.49,0:56:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was driving somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.49,0:56:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and a rabbit ran across the road
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.49,0:56:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,wham, the brakes went on
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.49,0:56:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,saved the rabbit's life
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.49,0:56:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and instantly I caught that the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.49,0:56:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,took claim for that
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.49,0:57:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,said I break the brake
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.49,0:57:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,no, this time I caught it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.49,0:57:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it had breaked itself before
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.88,0:57:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to break and save the poor little bunny's life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.88,0:57:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,oh no, it was happening of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.35,0:57:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.35,0:57:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is an absolute reality
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.35,0:57:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.35,0:57:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,exists beyond all time
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.35,0:57:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,space and dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.35,0:57:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth and reality of the self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.35,0:57:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of everyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.54,0:57:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we are all one and the same
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.54,0:57:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the self that is speaking to you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.54,0:57:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is your own self
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.54,0:57:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,just coming back to you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.54,0:57:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there is only one consciousness here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.54,0:57:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it activates what the saying-ness
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.54,0:57:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the wording-ness is going here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.54,0:57:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that is what this body is here for
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.54,0:57:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,what is this body bumping around here for
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.54,0:57:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have done without years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.54,0:57:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, how would you talk
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.54,0:57:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were just in visible space
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.54,0:57:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of invisible space
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.54,0:57:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't talk to people
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.54,0:57:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you did, they'd get spooked
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.54,0:57:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to look like an actual person
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.54,0:57:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and talk in verbalized language
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.54,0:58:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so that people know what you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.40,0:58:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,which takes us to the end of the discussion for today
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.40,0:58:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought then we'll have time for any questions
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.40,0:58:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll take a little break
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.40,0:58:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,if anybody has any questions
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.40,0:58:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we've tried to cover now
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.40,0:58:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,everything I think within the syllabus
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.40,0:58:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the first time I've ever spoken from a syllabus
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.40,0:58:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,now it's more difficult in foreign languages
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.40,0:58:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where you say something
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.40,0:58:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you're getting enthused about it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.40,0:58:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you have to stop because the translator
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.40,0:58:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,has to translate it into Korean or something
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.40,0:58:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and by the time she's translated
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.40,0:58:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you've gotten what was it I was going to say
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.56,0:58:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that's more difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.33,0:58:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.10,0:58:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so what I've tried to share today
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.10,0:58:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is an overall view of consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.10,0:58:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,creation versus causality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.10,0:58:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,causality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.42,0:58:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,illusions that the world holds
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.42,0:58:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that blinds itself
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.42,0:58:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,blinds it to what is actually the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.42,0:58:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the difficulty in spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.96,0:58:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because of positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.96,0:58:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there's only one enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.96,0:59:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to all advance of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.96,0:59:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.96,0:59:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,adopting a positionality
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.96,0:59:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that positionality then
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.96,0:59:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,twists your view of perception
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.96,0:59:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot see the wholeness and oneness of all things
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.96,0:59:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it divides them into
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.96,0:59:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,thinness and
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.96,0:59:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,dualistic error
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.96,0:59:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so we tried to define
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.64,0:59:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.64,0:59:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,duality versus non-duality
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.64,0:59:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,non-duality is the new dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.64,0:59:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking again at
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.64,0:59:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in Albuquerque in April
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.64,0:59:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,science and consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.64,0:59:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.64,0:59:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,science is knocking at the door
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.64,0:59:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the linear to the non-linear
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.64,0:59:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because advances in human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.64,0:59:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,are in the non-linear domain
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.64,0:59:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to thank you for being here
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.64,0:59:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll stay for
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.83,0:59:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,any questions you might have
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.83,0:59:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you get to get a syllabus
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.83,0:59:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and a certificate of attendance
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.83,1:00:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,on your way out the door
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.06,1:00:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.06,1:00:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy of this audience was 411
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.06,1:00:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,when we started the lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.06,1:00:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,it went to 421 by the end of the lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.06,1:00:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness level of a human being
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.06,1:00:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,advances about 5 points in a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.06,1:00:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and we jumped 10 points today
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.06,1:00:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we jumped 10 points
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.06,1:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.06,1:00:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the advance in spiritual awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.06,1:00:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,was really what you would get out of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.06,1:00:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,two whole lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.06,1:00:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the information alone does that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.06,1:00:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so we went from 411 to 421
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.06,1:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very big
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.06,1:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you see because we're talking about a logarithm
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.06,1:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't go up 10 points
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.06,1:00:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,we went up the log
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.06,1:00:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,10 points
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.54,1:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you who understand logarithms can explain it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.54,1:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot what logarithms mean
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.54,1:00:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but anyway it's a big jump
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.54,1:00:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,alright now what I tried to teach people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.54,1:00:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,is the technique of kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.54,1:00:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and some of these people
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.54,1:00:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ask specific questions
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.54,1:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the way to find the answer
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.67,1:01:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is to do what I told you today
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.67,1:01:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you just go
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.67,1:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is it over 200
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.67,1:01:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,over 300 over 400
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.67,1:01:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,like that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.76,1:01:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,now a lot of people like to know their own level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.76,1:01:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and I find this very useful
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.76,1:01:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,yes it's very useful
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.99,1:01:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to know your own level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.88,1:01:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you can just
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.88,1:01:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.88,1:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the best thing to do is to find somebody who's close
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.88,1:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so they're available so you can do it once in a while
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.88,1:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and just practice a little bit
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.88,1:01:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really not difficult
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.88,1:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's pretty simple
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.88,1:01:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason you want to know your own level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.09,1:01:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is it tells you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.09,1:01:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what lessons you're up against
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.09,1:01:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.09,1:01:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to know what you're at
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.09,1:01:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,tells you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.69,1:01:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what direction to head
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.69,1:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people in spiritual groups
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.69,1:01:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,are in the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.69,1:01:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they have gotten to the intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.69,1:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they're able to read and comprehend
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.69,1:02:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they're intellectual
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.69,1:02:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they've read about this now they're curious
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.69,1:02:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they've realized that there is something beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.69,1:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.82,1:02:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so lots of people in consciousness groups
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.82,1:02:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,all over the world
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.82,1:02:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate in the 400s
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.82,1:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the level of increasing awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.82,1:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.82,1:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,a very good jumping off place
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.82,1:02:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it's
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.10,1:02:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the trick there is to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.10,1:02:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is to stop
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.26,1:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,verbalizing and naming everything
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.26,1:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.26,1:02:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,experience its essence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.26,1:02:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than its definition
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.26,1:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the confusion of definition
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.26,1:02:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.58,1:02:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what a thing is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.58,1:02:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Korzybski of course
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.61,1:02:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Korzybski pointed out
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.61,1:02:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that the word is not the thing
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.61,1:02:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the map is not the territory
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.61,1:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which led to the development of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.61,1:02:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,along with Hayakawa
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.61,1:02:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Hayakawa from Hawaii
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.61,1:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,developed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.61,1:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what was the name of it now
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.96,1:03:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a whole movement
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.96,1:03:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway they had a periodical called Etc
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.96,1:03:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the point was to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.96,1:03:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,become aware
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.96,1:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that verbalizations only exist
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.96,1:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as a verbalization
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.96,1:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that you can verbalize something
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.96,1:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean it has a reality
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.96,1:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why there is no opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.96,1:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to truth
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.12,1:03:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that is one of the most profound things to learn
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.12,1:03:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.40,1:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is truth
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.60,1:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,only truth has existence
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.60,1:03:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,only that which has existence is truth
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.63,1:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is untruth has no existence
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.63,1:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so there is no point to fear it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.63,1:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has no existence
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.92,1:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's something conjugal
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.92,1:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,conjured up
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.92,1:03:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because we say
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.43,1:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a god there must be an anti-god
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.43,1:03:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is good there must be evil
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.26,1:03:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,this comes from a dualistic
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.26,1:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to reconstruct
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.42,1:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the dualistic universe for you today
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.42,1:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but we ran out of time
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.76,1:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the definition
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.76,1:04:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the thinking that a thing exists
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.76,1:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because there is a word
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.76,1:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is the fallibility of the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.76,1:04:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.76,1:04:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,level of the 400's
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.80,1:04:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that which has reality
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.80,1:04:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,has no opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.80,1:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no opposite to god
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.80,1:04:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I know how to define this
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.60,1:04:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,by really defining a kinesiologic response
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.60,1:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we said
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.60,1:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness only knows truth
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.60,1:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't know falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.60,1:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,falsehood has no existence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.60,1:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so how would it know it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.05,1:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,consequently if the statement you make
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.05,1:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,has truth it has existence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.05,1:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and consciousness recognizes
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.05,1:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,acknowledges existence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.05,1:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,by making your arm go strong
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.05,1:04:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,say it has no tooth to it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.05,1:04:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it has no existence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.05,1:04:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,because it has no existence
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.05,1:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it has no energy
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.05,1:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,it can't make your arm go strong
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.05,1:04:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,say your arm goes weak
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.05,1:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so all your arm is saying yes
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.05,1:05:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or not yes
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.05,1:05:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that is different from yes from no
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.05,1:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a very profound and advanced understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.53,1:05:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll explain it in a way
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.01,1:05:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'll get it rather easily
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.01,1:05:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,in a wire
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.01,1:05:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,either electricity is on
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.97,1:05:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or it's not on
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.97,1:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no condition known as offness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.04,1:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot turn on offness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.04,1:05:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,offness has no reality
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.23,1:05:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,onness is either there
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.23,1:05:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or it's not there
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.36,1:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the same with light and dark
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.64,1:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing as darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.64,1:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,except as a sensory observation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.67,1:05:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,light is either present
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.80,1:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or not present
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.80,1:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.80,1:05:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as an opposite to light
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.80,1:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing as non-light
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.92,1:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,light is either present
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.92,1:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,or not present
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.69,1:05:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's present strongly
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.84,1:05:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,it's brilliant
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.84,1:05:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is less and less present
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.84,1:06:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,we call that darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.84,1:06:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,darkness is not the opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.29,1:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of light
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.29,1:06:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such thing
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.29,1:06:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,just as offness does not exist
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.29,1:06:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you can say that water is full of offness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.29,1:06:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not full of offness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.29,1:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only truth
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.29,1:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.45,1:06:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,because only the truth is real
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.45,1:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing to fear
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.55,1:06:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.55,1:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the nature of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.55,1:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.55,1:06:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing to fear in the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.55,1:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because divinity has no opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.12,1:06:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.28,1:06:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that can grade
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.28,1:06:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,can gradiate
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.28,1:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is your awareness of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.28,1:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,of yourself and all of existence
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.28,1:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the clouds
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.28,1:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,obscure the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.28,1:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but they are not the opposite of the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.28,1:06:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the sky has no opposite
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.96,1:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no non-skyness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.96,1:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have to fear
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.96,1:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no non-skyness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.96,1:06:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.66,1:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,without the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.04,1:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of a Christ consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.04,1:07:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.04,1:07:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.04,1:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the darkness would be so obscure
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.04,1:07:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,one would never get to see the light of the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.04,1:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.04,1:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with help from others
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.33,1:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,from that consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.33,1:07:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we are lifted out of that darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.50,1:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the difficulty
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.50,1:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of what we are saying in kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.50,1:07:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of testing have you done
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.50,1:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to rule out that a person's life view
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.50,1:07:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or experience is not influencing the result
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.50,1:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the basic work out of which
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.50,1:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,power versus force came
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.50,1:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,was
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.50,1:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a dissertation presented to the university
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.50,1:07:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.50,1:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,well received by the university faculty
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.50,1:07:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,called
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.56,1:07:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,quantitative and qualitative analysis
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.56,1:07:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and calibrations of the level of human consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.56,1:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wow
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.56,1:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,calibration
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.04,1:08:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I always forget it myself
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.04,1:08:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.04,1:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.04,1:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that was a highly scientific
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.04,1:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,dissertation
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.04,1:08:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we used traditional academic standards
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.04,1:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.04,1:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.48,1:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,statistical analysis
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.58,1:08:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact I hired a statistical analysis firm
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.58,1:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they took all the data
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.58,1:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,ran it through their computers
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.58,1:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,P came out
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.58,1:08:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,P was less than .001
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.58,1:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the chances of findings being
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.58,1:08:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in error were less than 1 in 100,000
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.58,1:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or something
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.32,1:08:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so scientifically
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.32,1:08:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,those who are interested in it
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.32,1:08:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's available through the publisher of power versus force
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.32,1:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,called calibration and
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.32,1:08:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,oh heck I'm not going to say it all again
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.41,1:08:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.41,1:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it has the scientific data
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.41,1:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,for those who like P is less than 1.001
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.41,1:08:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and those kind of things
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.41,1:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,it's based on the null hypothesis
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.41,1:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,proving and disproving the null hypothesis
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.41,1:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,with valid data
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.41,1:09:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so it met academic standards
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.41,1:09:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have gotten a PhD for it
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.02,1:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.44,1:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so that was the scientific validation
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.44,1:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the clinical
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.44,1:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a clinician rather than an academic
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.44,1:09:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an academic person at all
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.44,1:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.44,1:09:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,clinical person
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.44,1:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually I'm called a mystic I guess
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.44,1:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,a mystic
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.44,1:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you know the person's
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.66,1:09:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,experience is not influencing
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.66,1:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how to verify it for yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.66,1:09:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,there's two ways that are simple
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.66,1:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you can put information
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.66,1:09:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you can put a picture of
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.04,1:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saddam Hussein
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.04,1:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or somebody like that
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.04,1:09:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or a mole discovered in the CIA
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.04,1:09:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you can put that in a envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.04,1:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and give it to a child
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.04,1:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,tell the child hold this over your tummy
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.04,1:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold your arm out
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.40,1:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you say this person's energy is positive
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.40,1:09:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the child doesn't know anything
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.40,1:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,about what's in the envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.40,1:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he never heard of Saddam Hussein in the first place
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.40,1:10:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so the child
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.40,1:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is the best demonstration for yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.40,1:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that the child has no position on it
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.40,1:10:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.40,1:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the child has never heard of Saddam Hussein
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.40,1:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or something
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.40,1:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can use a child
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.40,1:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.46,1:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the most powerful thing on this planet
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.55,1:10:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is the innocent arm of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.55,1:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocent arm of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.03,1:10:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,tells the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.16,1:10:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or the falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.16,1:10:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of anything in this universe
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.16,1:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that ever is or was
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.51,1:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,formidable
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.51,1:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.51,1:10:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and his little arm out there
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.51,1:10:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,defeat Hitler and Mussolini
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.51,1:10:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and all the terrible
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.80,1:10:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,beings that are out there
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.80,1:10:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,live in dread of the innocence of the child
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.80,1:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because it cannot be fooled
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.80,1:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.27,1:10:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is like the hardware
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.27,1:10:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ego is like the software
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.27,1:11:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but the hardware of a computer
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.27,1:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is uninfluenced
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.30,1:11:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,by the software you run through it
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.30,1:11:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the hardware is not influenced
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.30,1:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,by the programs you run through it
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.30,1:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it remains pristine
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.30,1:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.30,1:11:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as a self
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.30,1:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is intrinsically innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.30,1:11:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and as you advance in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.30,1:11:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,what you witness is the innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.30,1:11:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of everyone around you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.30,1:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why it's not possible
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.30,1:11:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to judge people anymore
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.30,1:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not within the realm of reality
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.30,1:11:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that each person is
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.30,1:11:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,uniquely
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.30,1:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocent self
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.30,1:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which then has gone unconscious
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.30,1:11:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and gotten programmed by all this software
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.30,1:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and now this computer
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.30,1:11:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks it's software
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.30,1:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's forgotten that it's actually
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.30,1:11:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's own hardware
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.30,1:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to be enlightened
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.30,1:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is to wipe out the software
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.30,1:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.81,1:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,oh I was the hardware all along
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.29,1:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.29,1:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so anyway you can prove to yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.29,1:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the nearest small child
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.29,1:12:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who is innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.58,1:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and so you can have him
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.39,1:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,tell you what mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.39,1:12:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,has never been able to figure out
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.39,1:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.39,1:12:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the muscle test itself
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.39,1:12:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should say
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.39,1:12:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is this person good for me to work with
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.09,1:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,yes verify it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.09,1:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because sometimes spouses for some reason
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.09,1:12:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,do not work well together
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.09,1:12:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had time to research it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.09,1:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I did research it one time
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.12,1:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I came up with an answer
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.12,1:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know what the answer was
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.12,1:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it was like the secret of life
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.12,1:12:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned it on the way here today
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.12,1:12:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to share it with you
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.12,1:12:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,jeez the minute I got
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.12,1:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what the hell was it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.12,1:12:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I knew what it was and I also realized
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.12,1:12:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and it came back to me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.40,1:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought oh golly
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.40,1:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to share that with the audience
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.40,1:12:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.40,1:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you experiment
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.66,1:13:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you say this person is good for me to work with
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.66,1:13:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,yes no
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.66,1:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,then you do the simple
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.66,1:13:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,your subject holds love
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.88,1:13:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you hold something that's not love
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.88,1:13:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's really very simple
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.88,1:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not really hard to do at all
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.88,1:13:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,various things may influence it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.88,1:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll find out what does
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.88,1:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,music in the background
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.88,1:13:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the environment
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.88,1:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the other things that influence it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.88,1:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because she always
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.88,1:13:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,she clears herself
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.88,1:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,don't look at anything close your eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.88,1:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you saw that if you look at something
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.88,1:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that's like a smile you go strong
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.92,1:13:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,when you look at something that looks like a frown you go weak
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.92,1:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just a visual image can influence it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.92,1:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so it takes a little practice
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.92,1:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a very good book
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.92,1:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Body Doesn't Lie by John Diamond
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.92,1:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's also got another name
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.92,1:13:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Behavioral Kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.92,1:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been selling all these years
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.92,1:13:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of paperback
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.92,1:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and that really goes into kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.92,1:13:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you know for me
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.20,1:13:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,kinesiology was like the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.20,1:14:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,telescope to Galileo
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.20,1:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Galileo wasn't interested in telescopes
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.20,1:14:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he was interested in the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.20,1:14:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm not really interested in kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.20,1:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,except for its handiness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.20,1:14:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very handy and if you have somebody that you work well with
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.20,1:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll notice that
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.20,1:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we very often in lectures
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.20,1:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you know we'll research something
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.20,1:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,right down the spot we've never asked before
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.20,1:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,let's ask something right now
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.20,1:14:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.68,1:14:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of this lecture was over 600 resist
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.68,1:14:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,700 resist
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.68,1:14:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,780 resist
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.68,1:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,750 resist
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.94,1:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,760 resist
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.94,1:14:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness of this lecture itself
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.94,1:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,which I promised I would calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.94,1:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is 750
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.94,1:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,750 what it tells you is what level of truth that is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.94,1:14:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what level
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.94,1:14:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because truth is only truth
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.26,1:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when defined in the context of its own level
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.26,1:14:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what's truth on one level
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.26,1:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is falsehood on another
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.26,1:14:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is only true on its own level
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.26,1:14:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not true on other levels
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.26,1:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of the great difficulties
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.26,1:15:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in spiritual and religious confusion
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.26,1:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is the confusion of the levels
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.26,1:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,things are quoted
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.26,1:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that are applicable to one level
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.26,1:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and misapplied to another level
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.26,1:15:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,onward Christian soldiers
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.19,1:15:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean that you slaughter people
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.19,1:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.19,1:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the courage of Christ is within you
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.19,1:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to face truth
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.19,1:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.38,1:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,misinterpretation then comes from
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.38,1:15:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,mixing levels
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.38,1:15:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,quick mixing levels
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.41,1:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritual warrior is not the same
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.41,1:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as the killer warrior
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.41,1:15:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the killer warrior is a whole different trip
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.02,1:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,now
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.02,1:15:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there are various
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.02,1:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there are various ways of doing
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.02,1:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this muscle testing
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.02,1:15:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,some people have learned
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.02,1:15:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the ring method
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.02,1:15:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you hold a statement in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.02,1:15:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,my name is George
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.02,1:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,my name is David
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.02,1:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the circle goes strong
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.02,1:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,falsehood makes it go weak
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.02,1:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there are ways where you can squeeze your fingers together
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.02,1:16:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so people have learned
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.02,1:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,different techniques
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.02,1:16:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you get intuitive about it yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.12,1:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if you do this kind of testing
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.12,1:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for a period of time
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.12,1:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth versus falsehood
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.18,1:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute you state the question
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.18,1:16:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you already feel like a buzz
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.18,1:16:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what it is
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.18,1:16:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,like when I ask her a question
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.18,1:16:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can almost feel what the buzz is going to be
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.18,1:16:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,she already feels the answer coming down
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.18,1:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,before her muscles react to it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.18,1:16:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,she already feels it go through her consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.18,1:16:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.18,1:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,just bicycle riding
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.18,1:16:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get really familiar with it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.76,1:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so there are those different techniques
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.76,1:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I once taught
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.79,1:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my arm to be a pendulum
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.79,1:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and false was this way I'd say
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.79,1:16:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am my own grandfather
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.79,1:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,no I'm not my own grandfather
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.58,1:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have two grandchildren
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.74,1:16:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.56,1:17:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.56,1:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then I have people that say they feel they are going to fall over
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.56,1:17:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have patients who are pretty
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.56,1:17:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,advanced in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.56,1:17:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute I hold a statement in my mind
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.56,1:17:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's false I feel like
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.56,1:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to fall over
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.56,1:17:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so everybody has these different ways
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.56,1:17:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a sensitivity
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.56,1:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that you train yourself to observe
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.56,1:17:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,see most people take for granted
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.56,1:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the space in this room
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.56,1:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,most people take for granted
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.56,1:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,their own consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.56,1:17:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.79,1:17:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,never aware that awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.79,1:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is a certain level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.79,1:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,they just fear
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.79,1:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you always see your nose on your face
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.97,1:17:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so people lose awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.97,1:17:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of awareness itself
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.39,1:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and they also confuse
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.39,1:17:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness as a personal event
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.39,1:17:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than an impersonal one
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.55,1:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite self
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.55,1:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you truly are is impersonal
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.55,1:17:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not an individual
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.64,1:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,separate being
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.64,1:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that rises and falls
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.64,1:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and has a name like David or something
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.44,1:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,life is impersonal
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.44,1:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.69,1:18:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrating something by yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.69,1:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,those are the various techniques
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.69,1:18:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people use the finger technique
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.69,1:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and with a little practice
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.69,1:18:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you get it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.69,1:18:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you just keep practicing one thing after another
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.69,1:18:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,until you get it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.01,1:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so these are sensitivities
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.01,1:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that you develop just by experience
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.33,1:18:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah that's great
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.83,1:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,wow what a profound question
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.47,1:18:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,we discovered that
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.52,1:18:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of various people
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.52,1:18:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,change over time
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.64,1:18:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this apparently has to do with
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.71,1:18:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the effect of prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.71,1:18:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,we've experimentally demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.09,1:18:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of prayer many times
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.09,1:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it has really a very profound effect
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.09,1:18:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody here who has done
