Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.36,1:27:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,up to the age of what I forget
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.36,1:27:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,remember previous lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.36,1:27:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and unless you tell them to stop talking about that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.36,1:27:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's imaginary and crazy
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.36,1:27:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,quite a few of them actually
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.36,1:27:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,do literally remember
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.36,1:27:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's as though the amnesia that's supposed to occur
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.36,1:27:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as you reincarnate
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.36,1:27:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,there's supposed to be an amnesia
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.36,1:27:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and when do you recall previous lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.36,1:27:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,real significant and useful
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.36,1:27:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we asked that just this week
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.36,1:27:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,once you hit 600
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.36,1:27:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's really of academic interest
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.36,1:27:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,before 600
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.36,1:27:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,put 600 on
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.36,1:27:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it is possible to actually recall
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.36,1:27:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and see the significance
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.36,1:27:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that who you are has been
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.36,1:27:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in evolution for a great period of time
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.36,1:27:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I found that out
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.36,1:27:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,especially about physical ailments
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.36,1:27:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,physical ailments
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.36,1:27:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,tend to be almost
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.36,1:27:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically precise
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.36,1:27:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to something that's happened
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.36,1:27:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in some previous lifetime
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.97,1:28:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to believe any of this yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.97,1:28:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just say use kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.97,1:28:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and check it out yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.10,1:28:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can say
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.10,1:28:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,this came from some other life
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.10,1:28:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,oh good what was it
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.13,1:28:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's fun
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.13,1:28:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of it
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.61,1:28:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,requires an open mind
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.08,1:28:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,a true spiritual student then
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.08,1:28:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,has an open mind
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.08,1:28:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and prays and says
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.08,1:28:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,do God please reveal to me that which is useful to me
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.08,1:28:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I can understand
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.08,1:28:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I can integrate
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.08,1:28:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that which can benefit myself and others
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.08,1:28:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's sort of like
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.08,1:28:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the third step in AA
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.08,1:28:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where you totally surrender your life to
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.08,1:28:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,God as you understand him
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.08,1:28:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you wait to see what happens
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.08,1:28:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and comes into your life
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.11,1:28:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so at one point a thing is very significant
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.11,1:28:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and at another it's not
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.11,1:28:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and what I'm telling you about today
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.11,1:28:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is covering a huge panorama of things
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.11,1:28:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,some of which may or may not be significant
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.11,1:28:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at a given point in your life
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.11,1:29:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you may forget about
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.11,1:29:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,or say they're absurd
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.11,1:29:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then one morning 10 years
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.11,1:29:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,now you wake up and you got it
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.20,1:29:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it happens to me
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.20,1:29:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,as I drive down the highway all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.20,1:29:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm driving down the highway and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.20,1:29:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,wow something is so obvious
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.20,1:29:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say wow
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.20,1:29:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the same with jokes
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.59,1:29:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.59,1:29:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard for me to stay serious in the world
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.59,1:29:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have a great deal of time
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.59,1:29:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,trouble trying to stay serious
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.59,1:29:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because everything presents itself in sort of a comical interpretation
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.59,1:29:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I keep saying
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.59,1:29:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,where in the world did that ever come from
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.04,1:29:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so life is a joy
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.13,1:29:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll just make one last statement
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.13,1:29:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll finish
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.13,1:29:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the source of joy and happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.13,1:29:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is it in the future
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.13,1:29:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.13,1:29:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,where is the source of joy and happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.13,1:29:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness and enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.13,1:29:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it's in the joy of one's existence
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.13,1:29:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,in this very moment
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.13,1:29:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.44,1:29:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to be aware of the source of your existence
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.44,1:30:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,this instant
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.70,1:30:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to be in a state of joy at all times
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.70,1:30:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,because that is the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.70,1:30:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of God is
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.70,1:30:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.73,1:30:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,at this moment
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.73,1:30:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so the source of all joy
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.73,1:30:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,joy is not in the future
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.73,1:30:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not in the past
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.73,1:30:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's right in the awareness of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.73,1:30:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in this moment right now
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.73,1:30:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
